Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,寄宿生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是住在外國人家裡的那種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪個國家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,英國！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要去媽媽的朋友家打擾一個星期左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過忍 你不是不會講英語嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分 還是能說一點的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,像Hello之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsudon之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,1020)}豬排飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那是英語借詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我會每天祈禱忍能平安回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡好像有個和我同年齡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 能成為朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,會是怎樣的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸回來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 多有打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這個孩子比較怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,直接進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對齁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好有外國的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是客廳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,盥洗室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有要洗的衣服的話就直接說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,7點吃晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還有什麼想問我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 那個女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好像……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,波比 回小屋裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 她想和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫大宮忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大咪咪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我忍就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字叫愛麗絲·卡塔雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,金髮！金髮蘿莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲一一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼快就打成一片了呢……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,日本的女生好恐怖喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能合你口味就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,甜點不吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,OH！有日本女孩要來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蠻有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我又不會說日語……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 可憐 在她寄宿期間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你就假裝是我妹妹 過來一起住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不對喲 我才是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 明天開始我就要去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐家好喜歡旅行唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,鐺鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,來 這個奇怪的人偶送給你做護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就算語言不同 一定也能心靈相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐老是說得這麼輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,來 波比 來這裡 來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子 波比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄癢我了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,波比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那個孩子有好好道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 這不是愛麗絲的錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你熱一杯牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,非常暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝 Thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 非常暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,作為謝禮 能稍微過來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是從日本帶來的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本來是想昨天就給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是姐姐幫忙選的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她說這個比較適合送給外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這個呢 要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～原來是插在頭髮上的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 我知道囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是要插在頭髮上然後捲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我卷～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我卷～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 沒能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,當做筷子來用也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 你會做點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要攪拌均勻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,過來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明天送你去機場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩花牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 花牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道規則
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,百人一首……笑臉福神？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 第一次看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她問你真的是日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,純度100％啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是櫻花香味的入浴劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這裡好像不習慣泡澡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要浸到肩膀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就是日本的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 我覺得暈暈的……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}愛麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以一起睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,日本是個什麼樣的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan…日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,日本現在是早上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是神奇欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡明明還是晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的太陽卻已經升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有種只有我們被拋在世界一角的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話題小綾大概會比較喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}啊 小綾是我在學校的……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}好想在未來有一天可以去日本喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙您的照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,之後會把照片寄給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Hello！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hello——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你好一一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,日本……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 快起床啦 要遲到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,忍～?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 快去上學啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 因為讀了一下信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,信？哇 航空郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是以前去英國寄宿的家庭寄來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是愛麗絲寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦 好厲害 從夢中仙境寄來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是英國啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是全都是英語 我看不懂 正煩惱著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說讀了一下嗎 讓我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 真的全都是英語欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear 忍～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是大宮忍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你可是高中生囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都之後再聊ㄎ啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這是第一次收到信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 到底寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法啊 給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我想是說要到日本來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害 綾能看懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,信上有沒有寫什麼時候能過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}哼 別辜負忍的期望唷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,陽子你真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的學校 高興 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高興的制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 忍 鞋子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 那邊的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 金髮少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請問您認識一位叫做忍的女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我沒有她現在的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是一個和這個人偶長得一模一樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你也太失禮了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔雷特同學 走這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦斯響板？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是個蠻歡樂的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的女孩穿著我們的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不 比起那個我現在不管怎麼看忍都像那個木芥子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你更在意這個喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大宮同學 今天也很有精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,忍！忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了 真的來日本了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是為了見忍而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲會說日語了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有認真學習囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害 但是為什麼到這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔雷特同學 先從自我介紹開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫愛麗絲·卡塔雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從英國轉學過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在才注意到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,信裡有寫了的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但全是英語…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在第二頁用羅馬字寫了一遍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,綾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然剛進高中就有外國人轉入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,頭髮和瞳孔都像人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對呀對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好想給她換上一身禮裙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,放在玻璃櫃裡欣賞一整天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是說笑而已啦 請笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,來 寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小路…綾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,豬熊陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,野豬的豬 灰熊的熊 豬熊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有強大帥氣的感覺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我 食物 不好吃 饒命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,棒讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那個髮簪真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這個是忍寄宿的時候給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 那個時候的東西你到現在還珍惜著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但我之前還以為髮簪是用來捅人的武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要當殺手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在日本的時候住在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是一個人來的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 我打算去忍家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…獨身一人 無家可歸地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,住到我家來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雖是陋室 但卻有我！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我本來就打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈 這兩個人真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小女叫愛麗絲 還請您關照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽明知道愛麗絲會來還保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是嚇了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想嚇嚇你而已啦 對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你的日語說得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,正座也好標準呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我學習了很多日本的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還穿過一次和服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,正座固然辛苦 但穿和服更是又重又熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,十二層衣物的重量 大約有十公斤左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我堅信只要經受往這種考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就能成為合格的大和撫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼辛苦的話就不用再堅持了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便坐就可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家裡不用客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 小小薄禮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 太周到啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在機場買的銅鑼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,日本貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻花綻放的時節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,來自英國的少女來我家住了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 歡迎來到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房間是西洋風哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,洗澡是用圖式鐵桶浴盆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是西洋風的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time～
